spring security provides applicatoin level security for out application.

authentication is basically the logic in our application which decides who is user trying to do something.

    there are various way in which this can be figured out.

the second step is authorization

    authority---have relaitonship
        verb
    role---are relaitonship
        badge

    GrantedAuthority is the interface beind authority and role

------------
authentication
------------
    HTTPBasic
    CERTIFICATE
    JWT(OAUTH2)

------------
authorization
------------
    webapps---
        HTTPFilter
    non webapps-----
        Aspect
    Aspect can also be used with webapps

